{"tid":1330040,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄，林卓廷 你地會唔會道歉呀？","createTime":"2019-07-18T11:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T05:41:19.000Z","uid":48544,"like":34,"dislike":305,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"21b2de8b38490af04dac0aae8a62c2d3f1edec20","tid":1330040,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"林卓廷，你影完義士相，講del咗相就算？<br />\n<br />\n張超雄，你推個轉移運動視線嘅修正案，分化示威者。<br />\n有幾多人為咗呢條修正案嘈咗半日，無論係泛民支持者定係普通人，宜家撤回左就算？<br />\n<br />\n日日講唔分化唔分化，原來到頭來係你地一步一步分化示威者。<br />\n<br />\n我想問：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><ins>你地肯唔肯為損害運動嘅行為道歉？</ins></em></span>"},{"pid":"66d61147a406712c61db982da4ed05851056b946","tid":1330040,"uid":226126,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43708d4a713afedf49c0e81750f5a4384b44b89c","tid":1330040,"uid":48544,"like":10,"dislike":54,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我係咁小氣架啦，係你地搞到無人傾721"},{"pid":"f569944f72b48f1c9e2b9e6bf35dae8cf94bf6cb","tid":1330040,"uid":228963,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e16308c44a9721e3673e8aa2e0c19ab654e92a6","tid":1330040,"uid":48544,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"66d61147a406712c61db982da4ed05851056b946","tid":1330040,"uid":226126,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"我係咁小氣架啦，係佢地搞到無人傾721"},{"pid":"081e0567bf16a4a50f2960a44cb3605ed2b76d5e","tid":1330040,"uid":48544,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"f569944f72b48f1c9e2b9e6bf35dae8cf94bf6cb","tid":1330040,"uid":228963,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"我等緊個日"},{"pid":"16f9dfd3acf2ad90d7228c039ce55f9688292b6f","tid":1330040,"uid":4808